	<term>system window</term>
	<definition><p>A <command tag="palette">palette</command> that floats above all other windows (in all running applications) on the system.</p>
<p></p>
<p>Unlike an ordinary <command tag="palette">palette</command>, a system window is always available regardless of which application is active.</p></definition>
